name: R2R
body:
### Welcome to R2R
This project is designed to help passengers to book Uber on confirmation of their train ticket. Passengers can book Uber from their location to boarding railway station very easily.

### Authors and Contributors
@nehanandwana and @pinasis are great contributors to this project. Please fork this repo and add your features.

### Support or Contact
If you have any query or need any clarification, please feel free to write me on mayurt20@gmail.com
